      <title>哥伦比亚的目标是实现 2020 年疫情以来最大的财政赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/colombia-targets-widest-fiscal-deficit-since-2020-pandemic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于税收收入下降导致国家财政出现缺口，哥伦比亚即将出现自新冠疫情以来最严重的财政赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/colombia-targets-widest-fiscal-deficit-since-2020-pandemic</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 16:49:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>露脐装税为陷入困境的巴西零售商带来些许缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/crop-top-tax-offers-bit-of-relief-to-struggling-brazil-retailers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[期待已久的对 50 美元以下商品征收进口税将为巴西陷入困境的零售商提供短期救济，因为他们将面临长期障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/crop-top-tax-offers-bit-of-relief-to-struggling-brazil-retailers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 16:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官裁定谷歌广告技术反垄断诉讼将进入审判阶段</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/google-ad-tech-antitrust-suit-will-go-to-trial-judge-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在联邦法官驳回了这家科技巨头提前判决的请求后，Alphabet Inc. 将不得不在审判中针对美国司法部关于谷歌垄断在线广告技术的所有指控为自己辩护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/google-ad-tech-antitrust-suit-will-go-to-trial-judge-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 16:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首次投票前数据显示工党捐款几乎是保守党捐款的两倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/labour-donations-almost-double-the-tories-in-first-pre-vote-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国大选活动开始的第一个正式周内，基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 领导的民意调查领先的工党获得的政治捐款几乎是里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的执政党保守党的两倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/labour-donations-almost-double-the-tories-in-first-pre-vote-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 16:02:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芬兰将通过多国战斗群加强对北约的立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/finland-set-to-boost-nato-stance-with-multinational-battle-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约国防部长在政治上支持在芬兰建立一支多国战斗群，负责守卫北约与俄罗斯之间最长的边界。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/finland-set-to-boost-nato-stance-with-multinational-battle-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 16:02:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投票程序拖慢南非总统选举进程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/voting-procedure-slows-election-of-south-african-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在任命议长和副议长的投票被推迟后，南非议员们预计将于周五晚些时候选举下一任南非总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/voting-procedure-slows-election-of-south-african-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 15:55:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院在枪支权利运动中推翻了撞火枪托禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/bump-stock-ban-tossed-out-by-supreme-court-in-gun-rights-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院意见分歧，驳回了联邦对撞火枪托的禁令，称在美国历史上最惨重的大规模枪击事件发生后，监管机构禁止这种速射装置的行为超越了其权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/bump-stock-ban-tossed-out-by-supreme-court-in-gun-rights-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 14:10:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙竞选致法国股市遭遇多年来最糟糕的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/macron-election-call-sends-french-markets-to-worst-week-in-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者迅速对法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙提前举行大选的决定表示谴责，因为这引发了人们对法国财政状况进一步恶化的警告，甚至引发了对新一轮欧元危机的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/macron-election-call-sends-french-markets-to-worst-week-in-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 09:53:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非各党派同意再次选举拉马福萨为总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/south-african-unity-government-partners-agree-deal-on-key-posts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在令人震惊的选举结果导致国家失去多数党后，南非政治领导人同意建立广泛联盟来组建下一届政府，并支持西里尔·拉马福萨连任总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/south-african-unity-government-partners-agree-deal-on-key-posts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 08:58:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰在瑞士峰会前努力争取南半球国家的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/ukraine-struggles-to-court-global-south-ahead-of-swiss-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦周四在瑞士短暂停留。48 小时后，他将不会返回瑞士参加乌克兰峰会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/ukraine-struggles-to-court-global-south-ahead-of-swiss-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 07:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
